    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hover-paragraph">
            <p class="success-stories">
                At the HEAL Foundation, we strive to bring hope and relief to those in need, and we couldn't do it without the support of individuals like you. If you’re passionate about creating positive change, we invite you to join us in making a difference through our ongoing projects and initiatives. Every contribution counts, and we look forward to welcoming you as part of our mission to uplift communities and inspire lasting change.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Content wrapped in a large light green footer -->
<footer class="footer-section">
    <div class="container">
