                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional content -->
        <div class="text-center">
            <img src="~/images/Locations.png" alt="Contact Us" class="img-fluid mb-4 large-img" />
        </div>
        <p class="meaningful-text text-center">
            The 100% Model - We exist to serve communities, not ourselves. That's why 100% of the donations we receive go directly to helping those in need.
        </p>

        <!-- Pie Chart Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <canvas id="fundsPieChart" width="150" height="150"></canvas>
            <p class="text-center mt-2">
                100% of our funds go into helping the communities
                <span class="learn-more">
                    <a href="mailto:HEALFOUNDATIONSA@GMAIL.COM">Learn More</a>
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action Button -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                <a href="/Volunteers/Create" class="custom-white-link btn-lg">Come and get to Know us. Come Volunteer and Support Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

